local UserInputService = game:GetService("UserInputService")
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local Player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local HoldControl = false

RunService.Heartbeat:Connect(function(delta)
	local Character = Player.Character
	if ( Character == nil ) then
		return
	end

	local Physics = Character:FindFirstChild("PlayerPhysics")
	if ( Physics == nil ) then
		return
	end

	HoldControl = UserInputService:IsKeyDown( Enum.KeyCode.LeftControl )
	Physics.Height = HoldControl and 0.8 or 1.25

	-- Movement
	local MovementVector = UserInputService:GetMovementVector()
	local SpeedMultiplier = Physics.OnGround and 0.33 or 0.1
	Physics.Velocity = Physics.Velocity + MovementVector * SpeedMultiplier
end)

UserInputService.InputBegan:Connect(function(data)
	local key = data.KeyCode

	if ( key == Enum.KeyCode.Space ) then
		local Character = Player.Character
		if ( Character == nil ) then
			return
		end
	
		local Physics = Character:FindFirstChild("PlayerPhysics")
		if ( Physics == nil ) then
			return
		end

		if ( not Physics.OnGround ) then
			return
		end

		Physics.Velocity = Physics.Velocity + Vector3.new(0,0,6)
	end
end)

local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local UserInputService = game:GetService("UserInputService")
local ThirdPerson = true
local LockMouse = true

RunService.RenderStepped:Connect(function(delta)
	local Camera = game.Workspace.CurrentCamera
	if ( Camera == nil ) then
		return
	end

	local Character = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character
	if ( Character == nil ) then
		return
	end

	-- Position Camera
	Camera:MoveTo(Character.Position + Vector3.new(0, 0, Character.PlayerPhysics.Height/2))
	
	-- Rotate Camera
	UserInputService.LockMouse = LockMouse
	if ( LockMouse ) then
		local Delta = UserInputService:GetMouseDelta()
		Camera.Yaw = Camera.Yaw - Delta.X / 256
		Camera.Pitch = Camera.Pitch - Delta.Y / 256
		Camera.Pitch = math.clamp( Camera.Pitch, -math.pi/2 + 0.001, math.pi/2 - 0.001 )
	end

	-- Third Person Camera
	if ( ThirdPerson ) then
		local Direction = (Camera.LookAt-Camera.Position).Unit
		Camera:MoveTo(Camera.Position-Direction*2)
	end

	-- Character transparency
	Character.Transparency = ThirdPerson and 0.0 or 1.0
end)

UserInputService.InputBegan:Connect(function(key)
	if ( key.KeyCode == Enum.KeyCode.M ) then
		ThirdPerson = not ThirdPerson
	end
	if ( key.KeyCode == Enum.KeyCode.P ) then
		LockMouse = not LockMouse
	end
end)

local Character = script.Parent
if ( not Character:IsDescendantOf(game.Workspace) ) then
	return
end

local Prefab = Character.Prefab
local Physics = Character.PlayerPhysics

-- Clone Prefab
local NewPrefab = Prefab:Clone()
NewPrefab.Scale = 1
NewPrefab.Parent = Prefab.Parent
script.Parent.Prefab = NewPrefab

-- Create a new mesh
local Mesh = game.Assets:NewMesh()
NewPrefab.Model.Mesh = Mesh

-- This makes the mesh match the players dimensions
function rebuildMesh()
	Mesh:Capsule(Physics.Radius, Physics.Height)
end

-- Initial rebuild
rebuildMesh()

-- If height is changed, rebuild
Physics.Changed:Connect(function( key, value )
	if ( key == "Height" ) then
		rebuildMesh();
	end
end)

game.Started:Connect(function()
	print("Game has started...")
	local Character = script.Player:Clone()
	Character.Parent = game.Workspace
	Character.Archivable = false
	game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character = Character
end)
